title: Space Ibiza Live-We Love Sundays Closing Party
description:
DJs Alfreddo & Paul Woolford

Exclusive to Atomic RG.
Recorded live @ Space, this is the official closing party with resident 
Dj&#039;s The Legendary Alfreddo & Paul Woolford. A very unique Balaeric 
sound and excellent listening experience for all fans of anything from
this years White Isle magic. Superb mixing and blend of music make this
an unmissable 2 CD pack. My personal favourite is CD 2 which really
captures the imagination and displays the divetsity of sounds.
